---
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL === '/' ? '' : import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="py-20 relative text-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src={`${baseUrl}/images/notes.jpg`}
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      alt="A notebook and pen on a desk"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Experienced Team</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        At Rooted Growth Behavioral Health, we have a dedicated team of Board Certified Behavior Analysts (BCBAs) and Registered Behavior Technicians (RBTs) who are passionate about providing high-quality ABA services.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg">
        Our team is qualified, experienced, and committed to providing individualized support to each client.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>